Version: 3.0.13-1

1. Upgraded TeamSpeak to version 3.0.13
IMPORTANT:
query_ip_blacklist.txt
query_ip_whitelist.txt
Previous server versions never supported DNS names in white / blacklist.
There just was no error about it and it was semi-ignored,
which however caused other issues.
As such there is now an error being thrown and the server is shutting down instead of allowing such malformed input,
which could result in problems and security issues.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

